name: Accordion Multi Menu
tagline: Simple, modern and easy to use vertical accordion menu.
body:
Accordion Multi Menu
====================
Simple, modern and easy to use vertical accordion menu. It is built with love in Tehran for using in English and Persian (پارسی).

Requirements
------------
You only need to include jQuery.

![Screenshot in Persian.](https://raw.github.com/cyletech/Accordion-Multi-Menu/master/screenshots/in%20Persian.png)
